tions in Macclesfield, Bollington and the surrounding villages. The Church Leaders meet regularly for prayer, worship, fellowship and discussion, while small groups of Leaders and lay people plan Hope’s priorities, review progress and relationships, and manage its finances.</p>\n<p>Hope involves lots of volunteers, many from the local Churches, in a wide range of initiatives which any one Church would find difficult to sustain. It encourages like-minded people to come together to respond to their calling and to share their passions to make things happen for the benefit of the community.</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #00ccff;\">Proclaiming the Gospel through Social Action in Macclesfield and Bollington and the surrounding villages.</span></p>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:4:\"html\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"56d05dfaf043c\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1514729526446\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:3;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:8;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"5e601e8d-1f90-49ec-b671-fb13c8d6ef10\";s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}}s:5:\"grids\";a:4:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"cells\";i:3;s:5:\"style\";a:0:{}}i:1;a:2:{s:5:\"cells\";i:3;s:5:\"style\";a:2:{s:23:\"background_image_repeat\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"no_margin\";s:0:\"\";}}i:2;a:2:{s:5:\"cells\";i:3;s:5:\"style\";a:0:{}}i:3;a:2:{s:5:\"cells\";i:1;s:5:\"style\";a:0:{}}}s:10:\"grid_cells\";a:10:{i:0;a:4:{s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:5:\"index\";i:0;s:6:\"weight\";d:0.33333333333332998;s:5:\"style\";a:0:{}}i:1;a:4:{s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:5:\"index\";i:1;s:6:\"weight\";d:0.33333333333332998;s:5:\"style\";a:0:{}}i:2;a:4:{s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:5:\"index\";i:2;s:6:\"weight\";d:0.33333333333332998;s:5:\"style\";a:0:{}}i:3;a:4:{s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:5:\"index\";i:0;s:6:\"weight\";d:0.33333333333332998;s:5:\"style\";a:0:{}}i:4;a:4:{s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:5:\"index\";i:1;s:6:\"weight\";d:0.33333333333332998;s:5:\"style\";a:0:{