04. She is kept very busy.</p>\r\n<p>Just Drop-In is open Monday, Wednesday, Friday from 1400-1700; Tuesday and Thursday 1200-1800; Saturday 1000-1200.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Accreditation</strong><br>\r\nJust Drop-In has obtained the Legal Services Commission Quality Kitemark and Validation by the Cheshire Council for Voluntary Youth Service</p>\r\n<p><strong>Finance</strong><br>\r\nJust Drop-In opened with a Community Fund Grant which covered start-up and running costs for three years. This expired in March 2004. Since then we have been using our reserve fund built up by local fund raising, donations and grants.</p>\r\n<p>The Trustees are now looking to secure the longer term future of Just Drop-In, which has now established itself as a focal point for the youth of the town. In three years it can be said to have helped many young lives, and in many cases has made a vital difference.</p>\r\n<p>We are always looking for fund-raising initiatives and support.</p>\r\n<p>Visit the <a href=\"http://www.justdropin.co.uk/\">Just Drop-In web site</a></p>\r\n<img src=\"http://open-me.info/hinec.org.uk-v2/wp-content/uploads/logo-just-drop-in-317-160.png\" width=\"317\" height=\"160\" srcset=\"http://open-me.info/hinec.org.uk-v2/wp-content/uploads/logo-just-drop-in-317-160-300x151.png 300w, http://open-me.info/hinec.org.uk-v2/wp-content/uploads/logo-just-drop-in-317-160.png 317w\" class=\"so-widget-image\">','Just Drop In','','inherit','closed','closed','','84-revision-v1','','','2016-02-20 14:46:12','2016-02-20 14:46:12','','84','http://open-me.info/hinec.org.uk-v2/84-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_ytazrs7z61_posts` VALUES ('122','3','2016-02-20 14:48:43','2016-02-20 14:48:43','<p>Cre8 is an independent charity based on the Moss Rose Estate in Macclesfield. We provide projects and activities for young people and their families. Our work is aimed towards empowering young people and adults in the local area to&nbsp;<strong>make change happen</strong> for themselves and also for their local neighbourhood.</p>\r\n<p>The Cre8 community is made up of a wide range of people from different backgrounds, who work or volunteer from full time to just a couple of hours over the holidays.&nbsp;From the wounderful, generous and passionate volunteers who are the backbone of everything we do, to the slightly crazy but dedicated and very patient staff team - everyone who has any involvement with Cre8 is a part of the team.</p>\r\n<p>Visit the <a href=\"http://www.cre8macclesfield.org/\">CRE8 website</a>.</p>\r\n<img src=\"http://open-me.info/hinec.org.uk-v2/wp-content/uploads/logo-cre8-317-160.jpg\" width=\"317\" height=\"161\" srcset=\"http://open-me.info/hinec.org.uk-v2/wp-content/uploads/logo-cre8-317-160-300x152.jpg 300w, http://open-me.info/hinec.org.uk-v2/wp-content/uploads/logo-cre8-317-160.jpg 317w\" class=\"so-widget-image\">','CRE8','','draft','closed','closed','','cre8','','','2024-08-04 16:41:57','2024-08-04 15:41:57','','0','http://open-me.info/hinec.org.uk-v2/?page_id=122',0,'page','',0);
