 (Reach Out and Recover)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li> Website: <a href=\"http://www.reachoutandrecover.org\">http://www.reachoutandrecover.org</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Founders: Jill and Vicky Millward<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>email: jillmillward@reachoutandrecover.org</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>email: vickymillward@reachoutandrecover.org</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>telephone: 01625 619106 </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"opacity\":\"css\",\"backgroundColor\":\"pale-cyan-blue\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-pale-cyan-blue-color has-css-opacity has-pale-cyan-blue-background-color has-background\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Core Food Pantry, Upton Priory</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Organiser: Fabienne Donbavand</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>email: <a href=\"mailto:pantry.upton@gmail.com\">pantry.upton@gmail.com</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>telephone: 07946 005505</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/people/The-CORE-Pantry/61551746876141/?is_tour_completed=true\">(20+) Facebook</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Website: <a href=\"http://www.church-of-the-resurrection.org.uk/pantry.html\">Church of the Resurrection, Upton Priory, Macclesfield - CORE Food Pantry (church-of-the-resurrection.org.uk)</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"opacity\":\"css\",\"backgroundColor\":\"pale-cyan-blue\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-pale-cyan-blue-color has-css-opacity has-pale-cyan-blue-background-color has-background\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"> Hope Food Partnership</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Chair: Steve Oliver<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>email: steve.oliver3@ntlworld.com</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>telephone: 07801 715572</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Organisation contacts','','inherit','closed','closed','','240-revision-v1','','','2024-07-19 12:02:48','2024-07-19 11:02:48','','240','https://hinec.org.uk/?p=450',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_ytazrs7z61_posts` VALUES ('451','3','2024-07-19 12:05:26','2024-07-19 11:05:26','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Our strategic priorities for the next 3 years</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li>Continue to provide an environment that encourages church leaders to meet together and to selflessly support and help each other.</li><li>Grow a stronger relationship with leaders and churches who currently are not active within Hope.</li><li>Build stronger links between the churches and communities that we serve, including through even greater sharing of resources, ideas and best practice.</li><li>More clearly communicate our purpose, plans and stories to churches and local communities including through greater use of social media.</li><li>Provide opportunities for existing church members to grow in faith through service and shared discipleship.</li><li>Create and deliver a credible, resourceable plan to reach out with the gospel message to people in the community (e.g. hold at least 1 town-wide outreach event pa and grow the Treacle Market prayer-walking initiative).</li><li>Re-draw our plan for social action, identify new activities and adjusting existing activities... to best meet community needs, especially for the disadvantaged and marginalised.</li><li>Keep things simple, low in formality, true and Spirit-led.</li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Strategic Priorities 2024-2026','','inherit','closed','closed','','371-revision-v1','','','2024-07-19 12:05:26','2024-07-19 11:05:26','','371','https://hinec.org.uk/?p=451',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_ytazrs7z61_posts` VALUES ('452','3','2024-07-19 12:06:10','2024-07-19 11:06:10','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">\'Strategic Priorities 2024-26</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Continue to provide an environment that encourages church leaders to meet together and to selflessly support and help each other.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Grow a stronger relationship with leaders and churches who currently are not active within Hope.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Build stronger links between the churches and communities that we serve, including through even greater sharing of resources, ideas and best practice.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>More clearly communicate our purpose, plans and stories to churches and local communities including through greater use of social media.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Provide opportunities for existing church members to grow in faith through service and shared discipleship.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Create and deliver a credible, resourceable plan to reach out with the gospel message to people in the community (e.g. hold at least 1 town-wide outreach event pa and grow the Treacle Market prayer-walking initiative).</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Re-draw our plan for social action, identify new activities and adjusting existing activities... to best meet community needs, especially for the disadvantaged and marginalised.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Keep things simple, low in formality, true and Spirit-led.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Strategic Priorities 2024-2026','','inherit','closed','closed','','371-revision-v1','','','2024-07-19 12:06:10','2024-07-19 11:06:10','','371','https://hinec.org.uk/?p=452',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_ytazrs7z61_posts` VALUES ('454','3','2024-07-19 12:07:28','2024-07-19 11:07:28','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Continue to provide an environment that encourages church leaders to meet together and to selflessly support and help each other.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Grow a stronger relationship with leaders and churches who currently are not active within Hope.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Build stronger links between the churches and communities that we serve, including through even greater sharing of resources, ideas and best practice.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>More clearly communicate our purpose, plans and stories to churches and local communities including through greater use of social media.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Provide opportunities for existing church members to grow in faith through service and shared discipleship.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Create and deliver a credible, resourceable plan to reach out with the gospel message to people in the community (e.g. hold at least 1 town-wide outreach event pa and grow the Treacle Market prayer-walking initiative).</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Re-draw our plan for social action, identify new activities and adjusting existing activities... to best meet community needs, especially for the disadvantaged and marginalised.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Keep things simple, low in formality, true and Spirit-led.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Strategic Priorities 2024-2026','','inherit','closed','closed','','371-revision-v1','','','2024-07-19 12:07:28','2024-07-19 11:07:28','','371','https://hinec.org.uk/?p=454',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_ytazrs7z61_posts` VALUES ('455','3','2024-07-19 12:14:01','2024-07-19 11:14:01','<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To grow lasting relations between the church leaders, and a sense of unity/fellowship across churches.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To reflect God\'s love for His people and creation through shared involvement in worship, mission and social action.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To reach out with the gospel to the people in the area, including young people and children.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>*Confirmed by the Church Leaders at our Strategy Workshop in January 2024.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Our Purpose','','publish','closed','closed','','purpose-2','','','2024-08-07 07:34:52','2024-08-07 06:34:52','','0','https://hinec.org.uk/?page_id=455',0,'page','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_ytazrs7z61_posts` VALUES ('459','3','2024-07-19 12:14:01','2024-07-19 11:14:01','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Our Purpose</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To grow lasting relations between the church leaders, and a sense of unity/fellowship across churches.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To reflect God\'s love for His people and creation through shared involvement in worship, mission and social action.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To reach out with the gospel to the people in the area, including young people and children.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>*Conformed by the Church Leaders at our Strategy Workshop in January 2024.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Purpose','','inherit','closed','closed','','455-revision-v1','','','2024-07-19 12:14:01','2024-07-19 11:14:01','','455','https://hinec.org.uk/?p=459',0,'revision','',0);
